      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In the simple case, a view is sent "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483620-viewwillstartliveresize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " before the first resize operation on the containing window and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483543-viewdidendliveresize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " after the last resize operation. A view that is repeatedly added and removed from a window during live resize will receive only one "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483620-viewwillstartliveresize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (on the first time it is added to the window) and one "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483543-viewdidendliveresize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (when the window has completed the live resize operation). This allows a superview such as "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsbrowser"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object to add and remove its "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSMatrix"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " subviews during live resize without the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsmatrix"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object receiving multiple calls to these methods. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A view might allocate data structures to cache-drawing information in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483620-viewwillstartliveresize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and should clean up these data structures in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483543-viewdidendliveresize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". In addition, a view that does optimized drawing during live resize might need to do full drawing after "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483543-viewdidendliveresize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". However, you should not assume that a view has a drawing context in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483543-viewdidendliveresize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (since it may have been removed from the window during live resize). A view that needs to redraw itself after live resize should set its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483360-needsdisplay"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483543-viewdidendliveresize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A view subclass should call "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "super"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " from these methods."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
